-message-to-the-people-of-hong-kong/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fanewspost.com%2Fanonymous-message-to-the-people-of-hong-kong%2F&d=LFOX9O72C3pH7rxPP1PUBwbFtlMfP7wF5OAPhGI7yCY%3D&h=67b7e2e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://anewspost.com/anonymous-message-to-the-people-of-hong-kong/</a><br />\n<br />\n最底仲有片，認真要睇！我覺得講得好好。<br />\n希望有人可以翻譯做中文，俾更多人睇到，我英文唔夠好可以翻譯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:47:36.000Z","msg":"[突發]匿名者給香港人的訊息<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1404323\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1404323</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n翻譯"},{"pid":"b9b78a386ac08b8b10171d4ae15831cbb9f2deda","tid":1405201,"uid":237597,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:49:47.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"3140e100b0a0ba00048ef78c74fcfaeafcf9978e","tid":1405201,"uid":123163,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:49:52.000Z","msg":"At this point, the people of Hong Kong should accept nothing less but complete and <span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">total independence</span></span> from mainland China. <br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"965cd3c06fe45a14356e6a1166b62c4248096a3b","tid":1405201,"uid":100046,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T08:50:21.000Z","msg":"There is no doubt that there will be agent provocateurs in the crowd, hired thugs that governments use to discredit resistance movements by painting them as violent and disorderly. <span style=\"color: blue;\">It is much easier to spot these infiltrators if the movement as a whole makes a nonviolent pact, because people in large numbers truly can affect change, but the masses rarely want to follow a group that acts out in violence, regardless of how many people are in the streets.</span><br />\n<br />\n睇埋天琦封信 講左咩，用腦諗下 爬緊咩山  唔好送子彈比對家！<br />\n<br />\n香港人 加油"},{"pid":"cb3c